content: I am quite impressed with the accuracy of this deck.
The only problem is that the Horoscope doesn't change unless I uninstall and re install the application to see Horoscope change for that day only and also there is no widgets for this application
app will not download buyer beware. free modle works fine

i gave it 4 stars because even though it's a great app I refunded what I paid for the pro version cause I realised there were no real upgrades in the pro version... when you do though please let us know ... up grades would be like conclusive theories after card reading .. especially on the spreads ..just to help the reader understand what they might be looking at or ... spread context ... like a brief about the spread exactly and what each card means .. and what spreads can be used for ...
